title: Madden NCAA 2010 (Sega Genesis)
description:
Madden NCAA 2010 

Who really deserved to play for the 2008 "national championship"?  Can anyone stop Tim Tebow?  Will Texas beat Oklahoma again?  You decide in 1 player, or versus a friend in netplay.

Madden NCAA 2010 features 17 of the top teams from the 2008 college football season.  And in the spirit of Bill Walsh College Football, Madden NCAA has full color team rating cards for all 17 teams.

One of the best Sega Genesis NCAA Football games of all time.

Looking for more roms or online play?  Be sure to check out the Classic Genesis Sports website and forums. More information available inside download.

Madden NCAA 2010 
(version 1B)
